title: Janelle Monae Interview and More
itunes:title: Janelle Monae Interview and More
description:
Wednesday 4/25 - Today on the show we had Queen Janelle Monae stop by, where she spoke about her new album, using the N word, woman power and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Noah Crowley, a high school student who used a racist statement to ask his date to prom and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
